6 UNEXPENDED REVENUES
7
8 SECTION 3. (1) The unexpended balances of amounts authorized to be expended by the
9 Higher Education Coordinating Commission for the biennium ending June 30, 2027, from re-
10 venues dedicated, continuously appropriated, appropriated or otherwise made available for
11 the purpose of administering and enforcing the duties, functions and powers transferred by
