13 Department of Emergency Management for the biennium ending June 30, 2027, for the pur-
14 pose of administering and enforcing the duties, functions and powers transferred by section
15 1 of this 2026 Act.
16 (2) The expenditure classifications, if any, established by Acts authorizing or limiting
